Safety and efficacy of ganaxolone in patients with CDKL5 deficiency disorder: 
results from the double-blind phase of a randomised, placebo-controlled, phase 3 
trial.

Knight EMP(1), Amin S(2), Bahi-Buisson N(3), Benke TA(4), Cross JH(5), Demarest 
ST(4), Olson HE(6), Specchio N(7), Fleming TR(8), Aimetti AA(9), Gasior M(9), 
Devinsky O(10); Marigold Trial Group.

Collaborators: Belousova E, Belyaev O, Ben-Zeev B, Brunklaus A, Ciliberto MA, 
